{"tid":2066310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"將軍澳便衣警遇襲案 13歲男童遭改控暴動罪","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:28:08.000Z","uid":211994,"like":16,"dislike":352,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"8984a4d2c8541bf84c82c8b80494b116c977b7ea","tid":2066310,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200616/ZV7LKXBIFVFQHM4L3HHCP7DUCU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2FZV7LKXBIFVFQHM4L3HHCP7DUCU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d4e970ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2FZV7LKXBIFVFQHM4L3HHCP7DUCU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=41d90637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200616/ZV7LKXBIFVFQHM4L3HHCP7DUCU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月13日網民發起十八區「神獸罷鷲」行動，多區爆發警民衝突。有便衣警員當日在將軍澳被示威者襲擊，伸縮警棍亦遭搶走。<br />\n<br />\n事後一名13歲男童被控參與非法集結、非法禁錮、蓄意傷人及身處非法集結時使用蒙面用品共四罪。<br />\n<br />\n案件今在東區裁判法院少年法庭再訊時，控方將非法集結改控為暴動罪，並有意提交至區域法院與其他同類案件合併處理。裁判官應辯方要求，押後至本月23日再處理。"},{"pid":"713b03a4b2b6461825616a0c49aaeedb7ae49b45","tid":2066310,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\